metadata.name: Portrait of a thug woman Brit and her 3-year old daughter Deva!
metadata.description:
2022  
PNG - 3070 x 3840 px - 12.9 MB  
AI + watercolour painting + digital collage

This artwork is part of a series called "Let the Matriarchy begin". It is a reprise from the original painting "Portrait of a Noblewoman Sophie Hedvig LÃ¸venskiold and her Three-Year-Old Daughter - 1817" by Christoffer Wilhelm Eckersberg (referred to as the "Father of Danish painting")!

Let the matriarchy begin!  
Against the historical traditions of art, this series represents women as complex, authentic human beings, removing them from their usual role as muses, decorations, trophies.
